{"uid":"cdca4f42ab0fa61","name":"test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_disaggregated","fullName":"tests.fault_tolerance.etcd_ha.test_sglang#test_etcd_ha_failover_sglang_disaggregated","historyId":"d248dc1297013ab844a0d53e027efd2d","time":{"start":1775682767766,"stop":1775682862001,"duration":94235},"description":"\n    Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries in disaggregated mode using SGLang.\n\n    This test:\n    1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n    2. Starts NATS, frontend, and both prefill and decode SGLang workers\n    3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n       - Terminate the replica by index\n       - Send inference request to verify system still works\n       - Restart the terminated node\n\n    This ensures testing of:\n    - ETCD leader termination\n    - Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n\n    Note: This test requires 2 GPUs to run decode and prefill workers on separate GPUs.\n    ","descriptionHtml":"<pre><code>Test ETCD High Availability with repeated node failures and recoveries in disaggregated mode using SGLang.\n\nThis test:\n1. Starts a 3-node ETCD cluster\n2. Starts NATS, frontend, and both prefill and decode SGLang workers\n3. Cycles through each of the 3 replicas:\n   - Terminate the replica by index\n   - Send inference request to verify system still works\n   - Restart the terminated node\n\nThis ensures testing of:\n- ETCD leader termination\n- Frontend/worker disconnection from their connected ETCD replica\n\nNote: This test requires 2 GPUs to run decode and prefill workers on separate GPUs.\n</code></pre>\n","status":"passed","flaky":false,"newFailed":false,"newBroken":false,"newPassed":false,"retriesCount":1,"retriesStatusChange":false,"beforeStages":[{"name":"event_loop_policy","time":{"start":1775682610504,"stop":1775682610505,"duration":1},"status":"passed","steps":[],"attachments":[],"parameters":[],"shouldDisplayMessage":false,"stepsCount":0,"attachmentsCount":0,"hasContent"